00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,000
The Balance Child and Learning to Enjoy Life
平衡的孩子与学习享受生命

2
00:00:06,209 --> 00:00:12,510
May I ask You what are the important points in the education of children?
请问 你在孩子的教育中什么是重点

3
00:00:13,827 --> 00:00:16,433
You see, first if they get realization
你看 首先若他们获得了自觉


4
00:00:16,640 --> 00:00:19,153
to get first time to that point of realization
在一开始便得到了觉醒

5
00:00:19,716 --> 00:00:21,869
 if they are already born realized there is no problem
如果他们是天生自觉的 没有问题


6
00:00:21,930 --> 00:00:24,078
but if they are given realization
但是如果他们被给予自觉

7
00:00:24,463 --> 00:00:28,139
 then, you see, they start seeing from a different level. They become the spirit 
然后 他们开始从一个不同的层次看 他们成为了灵

8
00:00:28,430 --> 00:00:31,165
so their self-respect, you see, awaken
所以他们的自尊 唤醒了

9
00:00:31,709 --> 00:00:37,193
Such children behave in a very dignified, elderly manner, you see. 
这些孩子的行为有尊严 成熟

10
00:00:37,223 --> 00:00:40,327
They talk in a very elderly manner
他们用成熟的方式说话

11
00:00:40,358 --> 00:00:42,253
