并且他们给出各种解决方案

12
00:00:42,753 --> 00:00:45,141
and they are tremendous people
他们是伟大的人

13
00:00:45,808 --> 00:00:49,220
But we have to guide them properly by our own behavior
但是我们必须言传身教恰当的引导他们

14
00:00:49,720 --> 00:00:52,728
how we behave. The greatest thing is, how we behave
最伟大的事是 我们如何行事 

15
00:00:53,051 --> 00:00:54,230
 that’s how the children learn.
那是孩子学习的

16
00:00:54,908 --> 00:01:01,153
We put the children certain to some tests, how they are
我们会给孩子些测试 看他们如何

17
00:01:01,633 --> 00:01:04,766
We find out if they have any physical problems; we cure them
我们发现 如果他们身体有问题 我们治疗他们

18
00:01:05,026 --> 00:01:07,099
They have mental problem; we cure them
他们有心理问题 我们治疗他们

