00:01:07,432 --> 00:01:11,071
 If they have any other problem, social problem or anything
如果他们有任何其他问题 社会问题 或其他问题

20
00:01:11,362 --> 00:01:12,518
we try to help them out
我们试图帮助他们摆脱困难

21
00:01:12,893 --> 00:01:17,091
so that basically if a human being is all right in the childhood
所以基本上如果一个人在童年是好的

22
00:01:17,560 --> 00:01:21,083
then fundamentals are all right for the child. The foundation is laid down
那么那孩子的根基是好的 奠定了基础

23
00:01:21,437 --> 00:01:25,793
Then to build a child up into a good quality is not difficult
那么把孩子塑造成好品质的人不难

24
00:01:26,084 --> 00:01:29,465
 So now we find great artists are there
我们发现那些伟大的艺术家

25
